text: Perhaps McKinnon’s most frequently recurring political figure of the moment, the Jeff Sessions of SNL continues to be taken to increasingly surreal places. There was, of course, the period when he was on Trump’s chopping block, doing anything (even sitting on his lap) to get back in his good graces. But now we appear back to the elfish Southern caricature boasting a devious side (and a tail). Thank goodness.
